Detailed Description

Used to get UserTrackElements that are stored in UM.

After the UserRequestPacket-header the format is (X = USER_REQUEST_HEADER_SIZE):
PosSizeComment
X 4 bytes Start time of interval.
X+4 4 bytes End time of interval.
X+8 4 bytes Max nbr elements.
